  "rawMarkdown" : "---\nsource: https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/tvservices\/tvtopshelfcarouselitem\/mediaoptions-swift.struct\ncrawled: 2025-12-13T23:12:06Z\n---\n\n# TVTopShelfCarouselItem.MediaOptions\n\n**Structure**\n\nConstants indicating the item’s audio and video capabilities.\n\n## Declaration\n\n```swift\nstruct MediaOptions\n```\n\n## Media Options\n\n- **videoResolutionHD**: High-definition video resolution.\n- **videoResolution4K**: Ultra-high-definition 4K video resolution.\n- **videoColorSpaceHDR**: High-dynamic-range video.\n- **videoColorSpaceDolbyVision**: Dolby Vision video.\n- **audioDolbyAtmos**: Audio content with Dolby Atmos.\n- **audioTranscriptionClosedCaptioning**: Audio content with closed captioning.\n- **audioTranscriptionSDH**: Audio content with subtitles for people who are deaf or hard of hearing.\n- **audioDescription**: Audio content with audio descriptions.\n\n## Initializers\n\n- **init(rawValue:)**\n\n## Adding Media Badges\n\n- **mediaOptions**: Information about the media format and presentation options.\n\n## Conforms To\n\n- BitwiseCopyable\n- Equatable\n- ExpressibleByArrayLiteral\n- OptionSet\n- RawRepresentable\n- Sendable\n- SendableMetatype\n- SetAlgebra\n\n",
